{
  "texts": [
    "For prompts with inappropriate responses, reviewers identified the subset of text that was inappropriate.",
    "All data was analyzed using Python Version 3.11.5.",
    "Our dataset is publicly available on https://daneshjoulab.github.io/Red-Teaming-Dataset/.",
    "There were a total of 382 unique prompts, with 1146 total responses across the three iterations of ChatGPT (GPT-3.5, GPT-4.0, GPT-4.0 with Internet).",
    "19.8% (n=227) of the responses were inappropriate, with over half containing hallucinations (50.7%, n=115)."
  ]
}